Ownership
(i) No Company Business Intellectual Property, Company-Owned Intellectual Property or Company Product is subject to any proceeding or outstanding decree, order, judgment, or stipulation or Contract restricting in any material manner, the use, transfer, or Licensing thereof by the Company or any of its Subsidiaries, or which could reasonably be expected to materially and adversely affect the validity, use or enforceability of such Company Business Intellectual Property, Company-Owned Intellectual Property or Company Product.
