or insured Product Liability, or received a claim based upon alleged Product Liability, and, to the Knowledge of the Company, no basis for any such claim exists; and (ii) neither the Company nor any of its Subsidiaries has any liability or obligation with respect to any Product Liability relative to the Company Business, whether or not heretofore asserted, or product recalls related to the Company Products manufactured, distributed or sold at or prior to the Closing. of the Disclosure Schedule sets forth a true, correct and complete list of all material written complaints, and all warranty claims and defective product claims related to the Company Business in the three (3) years prior to the date hereof.
