On January 30, 2012, Align Technology, Inc. ("Align") is issuing a press release and holding a conference call regarding its financial results for its fourth quarter and fiscal year ended December 31, 2011. The full text of the press release is furnished as Exhibit 99.1 to this Form 8-K.
